      "title": "",
      "body": "I went to subway before and the experience beyond horrific. The food was incredibly salty, it tasted as if they had just emptied out the salt can onto it. Ontop of this, I didn\u2019t even order the extra salt option, and I think that anyone who ever considers this should rethink their choices. The service was garbage, there was an Indian employee who, I\u2019m not attempting to single out because of race, but rather becsuse she was so unbelievably rude. I am flabbergasted at the fact she decided to talk rudely to her manager about me and tell me to go to the pickup station (there is no sign). I came in with my order number, and she went to check for the order, came back with a Chinese person\u2019s order and then asked if it was mine, despite the fact I SHOWED her my name. Most times, I would\u2019ve let it go, however she not only racially assumed me once, BUT TWICE, because after she asked for my name, I showed her again and she elft for a while and came back and said \u201care you sure this isn\u2019t your order?\u201d Showing me the exact same Chinese persons order. This is more than disgusting and I strongly recommend nobody come to this subway. Never again.",
